// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1933 — Mass File Rename (alphv)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a913381-a7aa-5982-9bb0-f795b1526141

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
